name: Pisces
description:
1/12 Zodiac Series ByAshraf.

Pisces is a zodiac constellation located between Aquarius to the west and Aries to the east. Pisces is the 12th astrological symbol in the zodiac, originating from the constellation Pisces. In astrology, Pisces is synonymous with feminine or negative symbols. Also a symbol of water. In the zodiac symbolized by a pair of fish swimming in opposite directions.
